Package: XIBD
Type: Package
Title: Identical By Descent Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lyndal Henden
Maintainer: <henden.l@wehi.edu.au>
Description: XIBD uses SNP genotype data to infer regions of the genome that are identical by descent (IBD) between pairs of individuals.
  It can be used on autosomes as well as the X chromosome and the results can be interpreted by several helpful plots.
License: None
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.5),
    data.table,
    doParallel,
    foreach,
    ggplot2
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
